<p><b><a name="Strength">Strength &amp; Conditioning Program</a></b></p>
<p>Our goal at Jersey Sports Medicine &amp; Rehab is to increase the athlete&rsquo;s physical and mental development. Our job does not include developing sport specific skills; rather we focus on increasing power, strength, speed and endurance while decreasing the risk of injury. Our strength program is designed to work all muscle groups of the body. The conditioning program is designed to develop both metabolic energy systems, aerobic and anaerobic, while increasing agility, balance, coordination, speed and power.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Work with our highly qualified strength and conditioning staff to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Improve athletic performance</li>
    <li>Improve strength</li>
    <li>Improve speed</li>
    <li>Prepare for competition</li>
    <li>Establish off season, in-season and post-season programs</li>
</ul>
<p>Our programs are:</p>
<ul>
